Ghoul claw%s	食屍鬼爪%s
Soulforge%s	魂鑄劍%s
You are carrying Rakeesh's flaming sword, "Soulforge."	你帶著拉基什的烈焰之劍,「魂鑄劍」。
Pot%s of Dirt	土罐%s
It is simply a small, clay pot filled with dirt.	只是個裝滿泥土的小陶罐。
Brass Lamp%s	黃銅油燈%s
The shiny brass lamp is engraved on the bottom: "Aladdin Lamp Co."	這盞閃亮的黃銅油燈底部刻著:「阿拉丁燈具公司」。
Basket%s	籃子%s
The local reed baskets are simple but elegant.	這種本地蘆葦籃簡樸而優雅。
Empty Pot%s	空罐%s
Compassion Fruit%s	慈悲果%s
From the branches of Julanar, you have obtained The Fruit of Compassion.	你從茱拉娜的枝椏上摘得了慈悲之果。
Waterskin%s	水囊%s
Your leather waterskin is crucial adventuring equipment in the desert.	你的皮製水囊是沙漠冒險不可或缺的裝備。
Cloth Bag%s	布袋%s
Powder%s of Burning	燃燒粉%s
From Harik you have obtained a quantity of the Powder of Burning.	你從哈里克那裡取得了一些燃燒粉。
EOF Secret Membership Badge%s	EOF秘密會員徽章%s
This genuine imitation brass Secret Membership Badge, with its secret code and secret runic engraving (so secret that NOBODY knows what it means), marks you as an EOF member in good standing.	這枚如假包換的仿黃銅秘密會員徽章,上頭刻有秘密代碼與秘密符文(秘密到連誰也不知道是什麼意思),證明你是EOF的正式會員。
Raseirian Visa%s	拉希爾簽證%s
It's your Raseirian Visa.  Don't leave town without it.	這是你的拉希爾簽證,出城千萬別忘了帶。
Container%s of Oil	油罐%s
You possess a small container of saurus oil.	你擁有一小罐索魯斯油。
Waterskin%s with Water Elemental	裝有水元素的水囊%s
Djinni Ring%s	精靈戒指%s
Silk Scarf%s	絲巾%s
This is the simple silken scarf given you as a token by the harem girl.	這是後宮女子贈予你作為信物的樸素絲巾。
Hand Mirror%s	手鏡%s
Black Bird%s	黑鳥%s
Poison Cure Pill%s	解毒丸%s
You have antidote pills to magically cure venomous stings and scratches.	你擁有能以魔法治癒毒螫毒傷的解毒丸。
Change%s of Clothing	換洗衣物%s
Saurus%s	索魯斯%s
You own a trusty riding Saurus.	你擁有一匹可靠的坐騎索魯斯。
Bag%s of Sand	沙袋%s
You are carrying a cloth bag with sand from the desert.	你帶著一個裝有沙漠黃沙的布袋。
Bag%s with Earth Elemental	裝有土元素的布袋%s
Inside a cloth bag you have placed the essence of the Earth Elemental.	你把土元素的精華裝進了一個布袋裡。
Silver Tea Service%s	銀製茶具%s
Pair%s of X-Ray Glasses	X光眼鏡%s
Leather Purse%s	皮製錢包%s
Your leather purse uses a drawstring for closure.	你的皮製錢包用抽繩束口。
Silver Dagger%s	銀製匕首%s
Emerald Bowl%s	翡翠碗%s
Rusty Nail%s	生鏽釘子%s
Levitate	浮空術
Reversal	逆轉術
Sorry about that.  The monster is dead broke.	抱歉,這隻怪物身無分文。
The large amount of metal in your shield makes spell-casting impossible.	你盾牌上大量的金屬讓你無法施法。
Your Dazzle spell doesn't seem to have had any effect on your opponent.	你的眩光術似乎對敵人毫無效果。
That doesn't seem to have done much of anything.  There must not have been a spell to Trigger.	這似乎沒起什麼作用,想必沒有可觸發的法術。
As you know, that spell is not usable in combat.  Casting it would leave you open to attack.	你知道那個法術不能在戰鬥中使用,施展它會讓你門戶大開。
Which way?	往哪個方向?
There's no need to get that.	沒必要拿那個。
No one responds	沒有人回應
You're at the end of your rope.  It's magic is gone, and so is it.	你的繩子已經用到極限,魔力耗盡,繩子也隨之消失。
You are suddenly, forcefully reminded that "It isn't the fall that hurts, it's when you hit the ground."	你猛然想起一句話:「跌落本身不痛,痛的是著地那一刻。」
As your mind thinks the thought of falling...	就在你腦中閃過墜落的念頭時……
Good thing the Powder of Burning is only activated by Magical beings.  Too bad you threw it away.	幸好燃燒粉只對魔法生物起作用,可惜你已經把它丟掉了。
Good thing you can't hurt yourself like that.	幸好你不會這樣傷到自己。
That isn't a spell.	那不是法術。
That's hard to do without %s.	沒有%s很難辦到這件事。
Uh oh!  You don't have any dirt.	糟了!你沒有任何泥土。
You don't have any sand.	你沒有任何沙子。
You have no more powder.	你的粉末用完了。
Your rope is so limp that you don't know if it will rise for you at all.  It's magic has been drained.	你的繩子軟垂無力,魔力已被耗盡,你不確定它還能不能升起。
Honor	榮譽
Comm.	溝通
Not enough room to view inventory.	空間不足,無法檢視物品欄。
You Have:	你擁有:
Golden Dinars	金第納爾
Brass Centimes	銅生丁
