The well-kept Plazas of Shapeir are octagonal in shape.  Windows overlook the daily goings-on, and alleys lead outward toward other parts of the city.	夏皮爾整潔的廣場呈八角形,窗戶俯瞰著每日的市井百態,巷弄則通向城市其他角落。
The crystal clear water of the fountain is a priceless treasure in a land such as this.	在這樣的土地上,噴泉裡清澈見底的水是無價之寶。
The cracked and dry fountain is a pitiful sight.	這座乾裂枯竭的噴泉景象淒涼。
You don't have a waterskin.	你沒有水囊。
But you do take advantage of the opportunity to quench your thirst.	但你還是趁機解了渴。
You fill your waterskin%c with cool, clear water from the fountain.	你用噴泉裡沁涼清澈的水,把水囊%c裝滿了。
The Water Elemental cooly responds with a wave.	水元素冷冷地揮手回應。
For your information, "Go with the flow" is just an expression!  Wave bye-bye, everyone...	順帶一提,「順其自然」只是個比喻而已!大家揮手說掰掰吧……
I am known as Jabir bin Ma'amar.	人稱我為賈比爾·賓·馬阿馬爾。
Ma fhimt.	Ma fhimt.
The merchant's prices are all too high.	商人開的價錢都太高了。
It is hard to steal when someone is watching you as carefully as the merchant is.	商人這麼緊盯著你,很難偷到東西。
Merchants only sell; they don't buy things.	商人只賣不買。
%s sells %s in the Plaza of the %s.	%s所賣的%s在「%s」廣場。
Please be more specific, Effendi.	請說清楚一點,閣下。
buy: unexpected CheckFunds result: %d	buy: unexpected CheckFunds result: %d
You pay for the %s and put it away.	你付了%s的錢,把它收了起來。
I have none of those today, Effendi.	今天我沒有那個了,閣下。
Alas, you will need to visit the Money Changer before you can buy something here.	可惜,你得先去找兌幣商,才能在這裡買東西。
Please approach me if you wish to purchase my wares, Effendi.	若您想購買我的商品,請靠近一些,閣下。
%s: unknown cue	%s: unknown cue
The price of the %s is %d centimes.	%s的價格是%d生丁。
Next time you break into a shop, make sure there are no guards around.	下次闖進店裡之前,先確認附近沒有守衛。
The guard says, "I warned you once!", as he hauls you off to the local pokey.  Now play it again, Sam.	守衛說:「我警告過你一次了!」便把你拖進了當地的牢房。好戲,再來一次吧。
The door is barred and your magic has no effect.	這扇門被閂住了,你的魔法對它不起作用。
Don't worry about closing the door.	不用擔心把門關上。
Just walk over to the door.	走到門邊就行了。
The door is not locked.	這扇門沒有上鎖。
You daren't try to pick the lock in broad daylight!	你可不敢在光天化日之下撬鎖!
You aren't close enough.	你離得不夠近。
This door appears to be barred from the inside.  Picking the lock will not help you enter.	這扇門似乎是從裡面閂上的,撬鎖對進門毫無幫助。
You're up to your compass in elementals!  You can't use your map now.	你被元素精怪圍得團團轉!現在沒辦法看地圖。
There's too much going on to take time out for the map right now.	現在事情太多,沒空看地圖。
